{"tid":1800221,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【新軸心國 】中俄伊三國今日開始聯合軍事演習，為40年來首次  (27/12/2019)","createTime":"2019-12-27T15:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T05:02:32.000Z","uid":236171,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"71f99dab3a181ff5fac4d210a2a466ef433bf2f4","tid":1800221,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T15:04:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-50923924\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-50923924&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPAoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=ed44e6c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-50923924&h=ba212587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-50923924</a><br />\n<br />\n中國國防部周四表示，中國、伊朗、俄羅斯在本周五舉行聯合軍事演習，演習地點在印度洋北部的阿曼灣。演習將持續四天。<br />\n<br />\n中國將派西寧號導彈驅逐艦參加。<br />\n<br />\n 阿曼灣是非常敏感的戰略航道，它與霍爾姆斯海峽相連，全球約五分之一的石油通過阿曼灣和霍爾姆斯海峽運輸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d9eca99fd817c0f0ca1c042aab47c42316332cc","tid":1800221,"uid":236171,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T15:05:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>開始玩歸邊了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9d14931ed85ccffcf37ae28d69faf9d5c3dda175","tid":1800221,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T15:05:54.000Z","msg":"（聯署）你班友快Ｄ同我簽晒佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1799015\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1799015</a><br />\n<br />\n你地又話好討厭甴近